top.value: Conditions - Technical Cooperation is provided free of charge to           the partner country; onlending by the partner country government to the project-executing           agency as a loan (splitting of terms) is generally not foreseen. Financially strong           partner countries are to contribute visibly more to the costs of the development measures           in accordance with their capacity.
